snippet.title: MAGIC MIKE XXL (2015) | The Moves of Magic Mike XXL Featurette
snippet.description:
Magic Mike XXL "The Moves of Magic Mike XXL" Featurette
Directed by Gregory Jacobs and starring Channing Tatum, Joe Manganiello, Matt Bomer, Adam Rodriguez, Amber Heard...

Three years after Mike bowed out of the stripper life at the top of his game, he and the remaining Kings of Tampa hit the road to Myrtle Beach to put on one last blow-out performance.
